      <br/>
      <br/>

      <p>
        In the extreme, the hill is a cliff, and the object falls straight down. In this case, gravity acts entirely
        in the direction of the motion of the object. 
      </p>

     <br/>
      <img class="img-centered img-size" src="ForceDirMotionDown.png"/>
     <br/>

      <form class="quiz_choice quiz">
